channel.title: IpkI Scape!
channel.description:
[img]http://i282.photobucket.com/albums/kk261/mr_bob_silab/pic20for20site.jpg[/img]
Al right, well, me and I vitiello I are making a new version of IpkI Scape. Here is what is done so far.
-All skills working and properly -Quests -Grand Echange -Dfs moves with you -Good economy -Good Security -Following works -Cannon works -Correct animations for things like range and mining -Skilling give you what you are supposed to get like Wood Cutting gets you wood and not money. -Daggonath Cave (dags also attack using mage, range and melee) - 60% -Duel Arena - 12% -Have started on Pest Control but can't quite put a percent on it -Have not started on Full Kalphite Layer or Castle Wars -Real God Sword and other weapon special attacks and much more...
I will add more pics as the server progresses.
